e\": \"In all of her matches, her opponent was favoured by each of the nine judges in the scoring system.\", \"from\": 701, \"to\": 799, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her matches\", \"from\": 711, \"to\": 722}, {\"ngram\": \"her opponent\", \"from\": 724, \"to\": 736}, {\"ngram\": \"the nine judges\", \"from\": 761, \"to\": 776}, {\"ngram\": \"the scoring system\", \"from\": 780, \"to\": 798}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 36-year-old's dance moves drew heavy criticism and online trolling, with the Australian Olympic Team rallying to support her during the \\\"devastating\\\" backlash she received.\", \"from\": 801, \"to\": 977, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 882, \"end\": 905, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_at_the_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999082215296, \"rank\": 9.17785884744038e-08, \"text\": \"Australian Olympic Team\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_at_the_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_at_the_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The 36-year-old's dance moves\", \"from\": 801, \"to\": 830}, {\"ngram\": \"heavy criticism\", \"from\": 836, \"to\": 851}, {\"ngram\": \"online trolling\", \"from\": 856, \"to\": 871}, {\"ngram\": \"the \\\"devastating\\\" backlash\", \"from\": 937, \"to\": 963}]}, {\"sentence\": \"During a recent stand-up gig, Barker, 50, defended Gunn and the originality of her performance, arguing her uniqueness means she will always be remembered.\", \"from\": 979, \"to\": 1134, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1030, \"end\": 1034, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"score\": 0.9831149677541856, \"rank\": 0.011949807446849186, \"text\": \"Gunn\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a recent stand-up gig\", \"from\": 986, \"to\": 1007}, {\"ngram\": \"Barker\", \"from\": 1009, \"to\": 1015}, {\"ngram\": \"the originality\", \"from\": 1039, \"to\": 1054}, {\"ngram\": \"her performance\", \"from\": 1058, \"to\": 1073}, {\"ngram\": \"her uniqueness\", \"from\": 1083, \"to\": 1097}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I saw some memes that were pretty funny, and, I mean, it was pretty surprising what she did, but I do not get all the hate, you know, like, I do not get like, there is a lot of people that are like 'you are a disgrace' and, 'you are a waste of taxpayers money,'\\\" he told the audience at Melbourne's The Comic Lounge.\", \"from\": 1136, \"to\": 1453, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1424, \"end\": 1433, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Melbourne\", \"score\": 0.9988008476183986, \"rank\": 0.0009152326297697026, \"text\": \"Melbourne\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Melbourne\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Melbourne\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"some memes\", \"from\": 1143, \"to\": 1153}, {\"ngram\": \"all the hate\", \"from\": 1247, \"to\": 1259}, {\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 1305, \"to\": 1310}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 1314, \"to\": 1320}, {\"ngram\": \"a disgrace\", \"from\": 1344, \"to\": 1354}, {\"ngram\": \"a waste\", \"from\": 1370, \"to\": 1377}, {\"ngram\": \"taxpayers money\", \"from\": 1381, \"to\": 1396}, {\"ngram\": \"the audience\", \"from\": 1408, \"to\": 1420}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"For me, I do not understand that, because I think at the very least, what she did was pretty courageous.\", \"from\": 1455, \"to\": 1560, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You could say what you want about her, but I mean, she knew she wasn't gonna win.\", \"from\": 1561, \"to\": 1642, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"She f***ing went out in style, man.\", \"from\": 1644, \"to\": 1680, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"style\", \"from\": 1669, \"to\": 1674}, {\"ngram\": \"man\", \"from\": 1676, \"to\": 1679}]}, {\"sente